themselves a keen eye.

04:18.822 --> 04:23.567
This is crap, crap,
crap, crap, crap.

04:23.611 --> 04:26.266
This--
this is not crap.

04:30.400 --> 04:31.358
RAW

04:31.401 --> 04:33.490
- This is--
- "RAW"?

04:36.841 --> 04:38.278
Yeah.

04:49.289 --> 04:53.118
- You Randall?
- Where's Bob?

04:53.162 --> 04:54.816
