Are you Randall?

04:54.859 --> 04:57.819
Yeah, I am.

04:57.862 --> 04:59.386
Come on with me.

04:59.429 --> 05:02.824
Picasso, he was being
harassed by German soldiers.

05:02.867 --> 05:04.042
Are you Randall?

05:04.086 --> 05:05.392
One of the officers,

05:05.435 --> 05:07.394
he saw the painting...

05:07.437 --> 05:09.265
...in Picasso's apartment.

05:09.309 --> 05:11.485
You can't hang
your own art in the gallery.

05:11.528 --> 05:14.618
I didn't put
that art there.

05:14.662 --> 05:18.535
And he asked Picasso--
he said, "Did you do that?"

05:18.579 --> 05:21.059
You can't get
someone else to do it either.

05:21.103 --> 05:22.844
Bob was relieved
of his post earlier.

05:22.887 --> 05:24.628
Bob would never
leave his post.

05:24.672 --> 05:29.154
And Picasso's response
was no, you did.

05:29.198 --> 05:32.419
Please, Bob's a nice guy.
He's my friend.

05:32.462 --> 05:35.335
We're gonna have
to terminate you as well.

05:36.684 --> 05:40.427
- Terminate?
- It's vandalism, Mr. Whitsey.

05:40.470 --> 05:43.343
No, this is vandalism.

05:51.481 --> 05:53.353
Hello, this is Henry.

05:55.920 --> 05:58.183
He's up there.

05:58.227 --> 06:00.447
Thanks, bud.

06:04.581 --> 06:08.672
- Go away, Dick.
- Hey, buddy, it's me.

06:08.716 --> 06:10.108
Redlocks?

06:10.152 --> 06:13.677
Yeah. Open up
the door.

06:13.721 --> 06:15.375
You may enter.

06:16.506 --> 06:19.857
