in here.

06:51.976 --> 06:54.239
I'm sorry.
I threw up.

06:54.283 --> 06:56.938
They fired me.
I'm really sorry.

06:56.981 --> 07:00.376
Hey, hey, hey.
Don't be sorry.

07:00.420 --> 07:03.945
It's okay.
It's okay, it's their loss.

07:03.988 --> 07:07.427
But I like it here.

07:07.992 --> 07:10.430
What, in the bathroom?

07:15.217 --> 07:17.915
Hey, remember
when Ma had to leave?

07:19.308 --> 07:21.179
Do you?

07:22.006 --> 07:23.965
We didn't like that either,
but there was nothing

07:24.008 --> 07:26.446
we could do about it.

07:27.229 --> 07:32.539
So what did we do, hmm?
What did we do?

07:32.582 --> 07:36.456
We moved on together,
and we found our feet.

07:38.327 --> 07:39.981
Can we do
that again?

07:40.024 --> 07:42.200
- Find our feet?
- Yeah, that's right.

07:42.244 --> 07:44.681
Find our feet.

07:45.334 --> 07:47.684
What are you smirking at?

07:48.816 --> 07:51.558
You should see
what I'm seeing, man.

07:51.601 --> 07:53.777
You're a mess.

07:53.821 --> 07:56.301
- Yeah, I'm a mess.
- Yeah.

07:56.345 --> 07:58.303
Well, I'm ready to go now.

07:58.347 --> 08:00.697
All right,
let's get out of here.

09:07.895 --> 09:10.550
Got it.

09:16.425 --> 09:20.560
You have the pleasure
of speaking to Maurizio D'Oro.

09:21.778 --> 09:24.389
- And?
- You must be RAW.

09:24.433 --> 09:26.304
I'm here to apologize.

09:30.439 --> 09:33.398
Look, I'm a lot of things

09:33.442 --> 09:36.793
and raw is definitely
one of them.

09:36.837 --> 09:38.795
But why
are you apologizing?

09:38.839 --> 09:40.884
May I come in?

09:40.928 --> 09:44.801
- Uh... sure.
- This is nice.

09:47.456 --> 09:49.806
Very well.

09:51.939 --> 09:54.594
I've come
to offer you a job.

09:56.465 --> 09:58.119
- A job?
- As I understand it,

09:58.162 --> 10:00.817
I cost you your job
at the Yellow Peril when

10:00.861 --> 10:03.820
I inquired about your artwork
hanging on display.

10:03.864 --> 10:06.083
I'm here now
to make amends.

10:06.823 --> 10:08.433
Oh.

10:08.477 --> 10:11.436
What's wrong?
Your work is good.

10:11.480 --> 10:14.439
You just need
guidance, refinement.

10:14.483 --> 10:17.834
You need moi.
I like your look, though.

10:17.878 --> 10:20.620
Ruggedly handsome
for a painter.

10:23.492 --> 10:25.450
Hey, Randy?

10:25.494 --> 10:27.627
Come here, buddy.

10:33.981 --> 10:35.852
This is
my brother, Randy.

10:35.896 --> 10:38.376
All right, and it's him
you owe the apology to.

10:38.420 --> 10:41.641
Randy, this
is Mr. Mazarino.

10:42.206 --> 10:44.165
Maurizio D'Oro.

10:44.208 --> 10:46.646
Maurizio of Gold, yeah.

10:47.647 --> 10:50.127
It's 'cause of him
you got fired.

10:50.780 --> 10:52.652
Have a seat.

10:58.005 --> 10:59.615
So you're RAW?

10:59.659 --> 11:01.835
RAW's an acronym for my name.

11:01.878 --> 11:04.489
It's for Randall
Andrew Whitsey.

11:04.533 --> 11:05.752
Of course it is.

11:05.795 --> 11:08.885
But also RAW,
you're more ways than one.

11:09.886 --> 11:12.497
You have talent,
but you need to cultivate it.

11:12.541 --> 11:15.631
You are but stone--
an uncut diamond.

11:15.675 --> 11:16.980
Once we have you cut,

11:17.024 --> 11:19.200
you will shine
like the gem you are.

11:19.243 --> 11:21.681
You will be brilliant.

11:23.813 --> 11:25.423
- Wait, what?
- What would you say if

11:25.467 --> 11:28.775
I told you I have a good friend
at New England Tech

11:28.818 --> 11:32.692
who can help you
expand your skills? Gratis?

11:33.257 --> 11:38.436
- A school for art?
- Precisely.

11:38.480 --> 11:42.919
Yeah, I don't know,
to me, school just teaches you

11:42.963 --> 11:45.879
things that
I'd probably never use.

11:45.922 --> 11:49.447
You're being pessimistic.
School is for people like you.

11:49.491 --> 11:51.449
There's nothing
wrong with me!

11:51.493 --> 11:53.800
I don't need your help,
and I don't need your school.

11:53.843 --> 11:55.453
- Wait, Randy.
- No, I just,

11:55.497 --> 11:57.455
I don't want to do that.

11:57.499 --> 11:58.892
I'm sorry.

11:58.935 --> 12:00.545
If you know what's good
for your brother,

12:00.589 --> 12:02.243
you'll see that
he's in my gallery

12:02.286 --> 12:04.549
tomorrow morning, 11:00 a.m.

12:04.593 --> 12:07.030
It'll be a shame to miss
the kind of opportunity

12:07.074 --> 12:10.686
that I'm prepared
to offer him. Good-bye.

12:10.730 --> 12:13.820
- Thanks for coming.
- Coat!

12:13.863 --> 12:15.735
Yeah.

