Can I be your custodian?

15:55.955 --> 16:00.263
A janitor?
You want to be my janitor?

16:00.307 --> 16:04.137
A janitor is often
a synonym for custodian.

16:04.180 --> 16:07.488
I have a service
that cleans for me, Randy.

16:07.531 --> 16:11.492
I would do a better job,
and it would cost you less.

16:11.535 --> 16:16.279
- A lot less.
- Mamma mia.

16:16.323 --> 16:20.980
One step back,
two steps forward, I hope.

16:23.199 --> 16:25.941
Are you sure
you want to be my janitor?

16:25.985 --> 16:28.988
Yes.
Yes, I'm sure.

