a prime position here

17:44.846 --> 17:46.587
and this place
is jam-packed.

17:46.630 --> 17:48.371
Ain't that too bad.

17:48.415 --> 17:51.244
- Do you mind if we join you?
- Mm, not at all, pretty lady.

17:51.287 --> 17:55.552
