with that woman.

18:10.654 --> 18:13.614
- Wow, that was really good.
- I think I can do better.

18:13.657 --> 18:15.616
No, please, don't.

18:15.659 --> 18:17.052
Well, look, I'm Henry,

18:17.096 --> 18:18.836
and this
is my little brother, Randy.

18:18.880 --> 18:21.622
- Say hi, Randy.
- Hello.

18:21.665 --> 18:23.624
- Hey, Chip.
- Here we go.

18:23.667 --> 18:26.105
That's mine,
thank you.

18:28.977 --> 18:31.414
Thanks, buddy.

18:31.458 --> 18:34.200
Perfect. All right,
man, thank you.

18:34.243 --> 18:36.637
Yeah, and the game,
too, Chip, thank you.

18:36.680 --> 18:39.118
Yeah, I got you,
Mr. Nielsen.

18:40.684 --> 18:44.210
Oh, Nielsen.
As in Patriot Disposal Nielsen.

18:44.253 --> 18:46.864
Nielsen as the trash company
Nielsen, yeah.

18:46.908 --> 18:49.432
