I said thanks.

22:00.884 --> 22:07.326
- And see you later, RAW.
- Okay. Good-bye.

22:13.593 --> 22:16.335
- All right, good night.
- Buonanotte.

22:24.212 --> 22:26.649
You did well today.

22:26.693 --> 22:29.086
I will have you back
on Wednesday.

22:29.130 --> 22:30.436
You don't want me
back tomorrow?

22:30.479 --> 22:33.090
Tomorrow you'll meet with
Maxwell von Hausdorff.

22:33.134 --> 22:36.877
- Sounds German.
- Tragically so.

22:36.920 --> 22:38.879
Well, why
do you want me

22:38.922 --> 22:42.186
to meet with German
Maxwell von Hausdorff?

22:42.230 --> 22:47.104
Have a seat.
Don't worry, have a seat.

22:49.716 --> 22:52.588
So he's a renowned
art professor.

22:52.632 --> 22:54.111
I told him about
your work,

22:54.155 --> 22:56.331
and he's
agreed to meet you.

22:56.375 --> 22:58.464
Possibly give you
a trial in his class.

22:58.507 --> 22:59.552
A scholarship?

23:01.380 --> 23:04.687
Tuition costs $40,000
a year, sweetheart.

23:04.731 --> 23:07.560
Not a scholarship,
at least not yet.

23:07.603 --> 23:12.129
But if he likes your work,
you will be auditing his class.

23:12.173 --> 23:14.218
Audit his class?

23:14.262 --> 23:18.135
Dear me, boy,
you will take his class.

23:19.180 --> 23:20.921
But I don't have
enough money.

23:20.964 --> 23:23.619
You'll be
auditing the class!

23:25.534 --> 23:27.928
Which means you
will take it for free

23:27.971 --> 23:31.410
for the time being,
but you won't be enrolled.

23:40.201 --> 23:42.159
So you're the boy

23:42.203 --> 23:46.250
Maurizio's been
raving about.

23:46.294 --> 23:49.428
I believe you have
something for me.

23:53.432 --> 23:56.739
Ah, let's take
a look!

24:00.003 --> 24:02.441
Ah ah.

24:03.311 --> 24:09.448
Yeah. Oh.
Have you anything else?

24:13.234 --> 24:14.670
Uh...

24:16.019 --> 24:17.934
Uh-huh.

24:20.023 --> 24:23.984
Oh, now
this one interests me.

24:24.027 --> 24:28.292
- What is that?
- That, a cocktail napkin.

24:28.336 --> 24:30.686
Yeah, indeed,
but what is the work that

24:30.730 --> 24:34.560
