- Sweet Sienna.

24:34.603 --> 24:39.303
Oh, yeah.
Almost a found art quality.

24:39.347 --> 24:42.655
A touch of realism.
A genuine rare.

24:42.698 --> 24:45.005
Strong angles.

24:45.048 --> 24:49.792
