of Victorian charcoal.

24:49.836 --> 24:55.232
Und how did you create
this red and yellow hues?

24:55.276 --> 24:57.496
Ketchup and mustard.

25:07.070 --> 25:09.595
Yeah, yeah.

25:09.638 --> 25:13.033
Very good, I think

25:13.076 --> 25:16.036
you can audit my class
if you wish.

25:16.079 --> 25:18.604
A special session has
already begun,

25:18.647 --> 25:23.260
but I believe I can
bring you up to speed.

25:23.304 --> 25:29.049
So right here,
Monday morning, 11:30 a.m.

25:29.092 --> 25:30.485
- Don't be late.
- Yeah.

25:30.529 --> 25:32.705
That should be
good, yeah.

25:32.748 --> 25:35.272
- Okay. Thank you. Thank-- okay.
- All right.

25:35.316 --> 25:37.492
- Yeah, yeah.
- The whole point of this

25:37.536 --> 25:40.147
game is we have
the stick in the hand, right?

25:40.190 --> 25:41.757
See how long
and hard, right?

