53:45.439 --> 53:50.183
Baseball? So you think baseball
is more important than art?

53:50.227 --> 53:52.403
Of course not,
but I was with Red--

53:52.446 --> 53:55.057
I don't care
who you were with.

53:55.101 --> 53:56.537
If you miss one more class,

53:56.581 --> 53:59.758
your time here
is done. Verstehe?

53:59.801 --> 54:02.456
Get, get, get!

54:11.117 --> 54:14.207
- Buonasera, Randall.
- Mr. Gold.

54:14.251 --> 54:16.340
Come with me.

54:16.383 --> 54:18.429
Have you heard of the artist
Mauricio Callegari?

54:18.472 --> 54:20.779
Painted
Il Trágico, 1879.

54:20.822 --> 54:23.434
Molto bene.
And only Il Trágico.

54:23.477 --> 54:24.783
Do you know why?

54:24.826 --> 54:27.089
- No.
- Because he was caught

54:27.133 --> 54:29.222
sleeping with
his patron's wife.

54:29.266 --> 54:31.790
His patron
then cut his penis off

54:31.833 --> 54:34.009
and slipped the knife
into his belly

54:34.053 --> 54:37.274
and spilled his entrails
all over the piazza.

54:38.275 --> 54:42.104
The point being is
many men's downfall

54:42.148 --> 54:44.106
