It's all one thing.

01:01:02.223 --> 01:01:05.183
It's not-- yeah.
It's just one, yeah.

01:01:05.226 --> 01:01:06.750
- It's not a--
- It's okay.

01:01:06.793 --> 01:01:12.407
It's okay.
I'm sorry, sweetheart.

01:01:14.540 --> 01:01:19.414
Don't be sorry.
Autism, it's what I have.

01:01:19.458 --> 01:01:25.899
It's not who I am.
I'm just-- I'm just Randy.

01:01:25.943 --> 01:01:31.209
Randy. I will give you
a hug right now,

01:01:31.252 --> 01:01:34.212
but I suppose that
will make you uncomfortable.

01:01:34.255 --> 01:01:37.519
- You can do it for two seconds.
- Cool.

01:01:37.563 --> 01:01:41.698
- Two seconds, okay.
